00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,560
Please.

35
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,880
Can you give this to my husband?

36
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,960
The "zi" in Jiang Yingzi's original name

37
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:13,880
means "son."

38
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,080
Her mother died early.

39
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:15,960
Her father

40
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,280
was an abusive drunk,
and valued sons over daughters.

41
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,680
At 14, she ran away after being beaten,

42
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,200
dropped out of school,
and came to Halan.

43
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,520
She left in 1983.

44
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,440
After that,

45
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:28,400
she disappeared for a long time.

46
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,120
Until 1989,

47
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,520
she gave birth to a girl
in Huazhou when she was unmarried.

48
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:36,440
The father's name was left blank.

49
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,800
Her father died in 1993,

50
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,760
and she returned to Halan
and opened the Future Pharmacy.

51
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,800
Six months later,
she married Wang Jianmin.

52
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,880
No wonder I felt something was off

53
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:49,200
between Wang Jianmin and his daughter.

54
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:50,960
Turns out
she's not his biological child.

55
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:54,480
The maternity hospital
where she gave birth

56
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,480
is very famous in Huazhou.

57
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,440
People who give birth there

58
