87
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,640
only their lawyer

88
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,280
can visit.

89
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,440
I'm afraid

90
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,920
I can't help you.

91
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,000
Sorry.

92
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,640
Xin, slow down.

93
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,520
There's no slowing down here.

94
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:30,160
Bei, quick,

95
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:30,880
give me a hand.

96
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:31,600
Where are you going?

97
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,880
Help me find some case files.

98
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,400
Hurry up, the files.

99
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:37,560
Be careful of your legs.

100
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,280
Back when Song Kang was the boss
in Halan,

101
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,200
he had several mistresses.

102
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:44,400
When the crackdown came, they ran.

103
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:49,280
Only one mistress stayed loyal,

104
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,240
and ran with him.

105
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:52,160
But they were using fake IDs,

106
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:54,000
so we couldn't figure out who they were.

107
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,760
Given what we know now,

108
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:57,680
it's Jiang Yingzi.

109
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:02,680
Both Jiang Yingzi and Song Kang

110
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,600
left Halan in 1983.

111
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,000
The timeline fits.

112
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:07,240
When Song Kang was arrested in Huazhou,

113
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,880
there was a woman with him.

114
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:12,080
But since she wasn't involved in drugs,

115
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,000
she was released.

116
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:15,800
If they were together

117
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:17,160
from 1983 to 1993,

118
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,680
then Mao must be Song Kang's child.

119
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:22,360
Jiang Yingzi's quite an actress.

120
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,200
She looks like

121
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:30,000
a regular housewife,

122
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:33,920
but she was the mistress of a drug lord.

123
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,040
Ordinary conniving women

124
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:39,960
couldn't pretend so well.

125
00:08:42,920 --> 00:08:44,640
Is it possible

126
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:46,920
that before Song Kang was arrested,

127
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:50,680
Jiang Yingzi already had the recipe
for meth?

128
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,040
She might've modified it,

129
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:54,400
which led to the creation of Lucifer.

130
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,400
That's very likely.

131
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,360
Is she...?

132
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,960
We never considered the possibility

133
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,440
that Mr. Ma

134
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,960
could be a woman.

135
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:15,760
Li Wenlong was Song Kang's trusted man.

136
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:18,720
After he got out from the prison,
he avenged Song.

137
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,000
Such a person wouldn't abandon

138
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,120
the widow and orphan Song left behind.

139
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,600
So,

140
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,240
from now on,

141
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:30,520
we'll keep a close watch
on Li Wenlong and Jiang Yingzi.

142
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,040
Given their past relationship,

143
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:35,800
and the fact that they're both in Halan,

144
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:38,800
they're bound to be in contact.

145
00:09:42,140 --> 00:09:45,740
[Mr. Ma, Jiang Yingzi]

146
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:48,480
If Jiang Yingzi is Mr. Ma,

147
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,520
then what about Wang Jianmin?

148
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:52,800
Is he her accomplice,
or has he been fooled too?

149
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:53,840
Probably not.

150
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:56,120
We've dug into
Wang Jianmin's background thoroughly.

151
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,560
I've interacted with him several times,

152
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,080
and apart from his wife Jiang Yingzi,

153
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:02,320
there's nothing suspicious about him.

154
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,400
Do you think

155
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:06,640
Jiang Xiaohai knows

156
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:08,320
that his sister is Mr. Ma?

157
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:10,720
Could he be involved
in the drug trafficking too?

158
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:49,840
Alright, stop sweeping.

159
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:53,200
The floor's cleaner than your broom now.

160
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,240
You've been quiet since you got home.

161
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:02,280
That's not like you.

162
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:06,120
The dust outside

163
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,760
is bad today.

164
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:09,200
My throat hurts when I talk.

165
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:11,360
But you won't talk in the room, either.

166
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:18,520
When Xiaoguang brought up Jiang Xiaohai,

167
00:11:19,280 --> 00:11:21,240
your brows furrowed so hard.

168
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:24,680
Ever since you
and Jiang Xiaohai got drunk that night

169
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,680
and had to be carried home,

170
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:28,480
you two seem a lot closer.

171
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,760
You're always at this place
whenever you are free.

172
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,720
Are you worried he's involved in drugs?

173
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:54,920
Jiang Xiaohai is Lele.

174
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,640
No wonder.

175
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,200
When it comes to Lele,

176
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:23,760
