177
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,920
I should've been happy

178
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:32,120
to find out that he was alive.

179
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:34,520
However,

180
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:37,520
