181
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,640
is involved in drugs.

182
00:12:40,680 --> 00:12:42,160
What a mess.

183
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,600
I know,

184
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,400
to Lele,

185
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,960
you've always felt guilty.

186
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,360
But tell me

187
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:59,920
if you discover
that Jiang Xiaohai is really involved,

188
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:03,760
what will you do?

189
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:11,400
I care about him

190
00:13:11,560 --> 00:13:13,520
because I do feel I owe him.

191
00:13:14,640 --> 00:13:15,960
As his big brother,

192
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:18,720
