for guiding him to be a good man.

193
00:13:22,880 --> 00:13:23,680
But

194
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:27,760
if one day,

195
00:13:27,760 --> 00:13:29,520
I find out he's really involved,

196
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:33,520
then he's breaking the law.

197
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,920
If I'm forced to choose
between being a good brother

198
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:39,760
and a good police,

199
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:44,440
I have to choose being a good police.

200
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,240
This isn't something I can get wrong.

201
00:13:56,920 --> 00:13:58,680
Alright, stop sweeping.

202
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,160
Let's go home.

203
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,000
I'll go talk to him tomorrow

204
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,840
and see what's going on.

205
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,200
Hai.

206
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,000
You come to see my godfather?

207
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:43,720
No.

208
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:46,200
Hai,

209
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,240
