233
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:42,520
Take a look.

234
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:46,640
This is called "Scholar's Pill."

235
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:48,600
It boosts concentration.

236
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:50,040
Take one,

237
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:52,400
