244
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:18,120
but it's in very small amounts.

245
00:16:26,080 --> 00:16:28,320
I didn't know you had the guts

246
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:30,200
to mess with meth.

247
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:33,360
You know what happened to

248
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,320
