when he was in trouble?

266
00:17:13,600 --> 00:17:15,160
You ran away, didn't you?

267
00:17:15,840 --> 00:17:18,320
These days, money is everything,

268
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:19,440
Hai.

269
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:23,000
I can't work with you.

270
